flowchart TD
    A([User visits app]) --> B[Upload .docx file]
    B --> C{Valid .docx?}
    C -- No --> D[Show .docx-only error]
    D --> B

    C -- Yes --> E[Parse document\nmammoth.js → HTML + paragraph objects\nJSZip → raw XML + relationships]

    E --> F[Extract metadata\nWord core properties:\ntitle, author, subject, description]

    E --> G[Run auto-fixes silently\nRemove CDC/DGHT editorial scaffolding\nRelocate tagline if needed\nOther silent corrections]

    F --> H
    G --> H

    H[Run rule engine\nChecks execute sequentially]

    H --> H1[Structure checks\nHeadings, step order,\nsection presence]
    H --> H2[Formatting checks\nBold, lists, tables,\ncaptions, footnotes]
    H --> H3[Metadata checks\nTitle, author, subject,\ndescription fields]
    H --> H4[Link checks\nBroken links, anchors,\nURL format]
    H --> H5[Content checks\nDate formats, tagline,\nkey facts section]

    H1 & H2 & H3 & H4 & H5 --> I[Aggregate results\nGroup by severity:\nError · Warning · Suggestion]

    I --> J{Any issues found?}

    J -- No --> K([Show: All checks passed\nReady for design handoff])

    J -- Yes --> L[Display Summary page\nStat cards by severity\nTotal issue count]

    L --> M[User reviews issues\nFiltered by severity\nLocation: nearest heading]

    M --> N{Issue has\nauto-fix?}

    N -- Yes --> O[User accepts fix\nAccepted fix stored for export]
    N -- No --> P[User dismisses issue\nor corrects manually in Word]

    O --> Q
    P --> Q

    Q{More issues\nto review?}
    Q -- Yes --> M
    Q -- No --> R[Export fixed .docx\nJSZip reassembles file\nwith accepted patches]

    R --> S([Download ready\nHand off to designer])

    style A fill:#1b4332,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style S fill:#1b4332,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style K fill:#1b4332,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style D fill:#c0392b,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style G fill:#2c3e50,color:#fff,stroke:#555
